id: pm-izid
title: Harden afterCommand coverage and GitHub code-scanning visibility
description: "Continue open epics with one scoped delivery: harden afterCommand affected-item runtime coverage and close the GitHub code-scanning reporting gap so gh-based security triage has complete signals."
type: Task
status: in_progress
priority: 1
